'''Cyber-vision''' was a technology which allowed the blind to see through [[Cybernetics/Legends|cybernetics]]. [[Orman Tagge/Legends|Orman Tagge]] employed such technology to see after he was blinded by [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Darth Vader's]] [[Lightsaber/Legends|lightsaber]].

